Class ShowSignatureCaptureResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.six.timapi.ShowSignatureCaptureResponse

  • public class ShowSignatureCaptureResponse
extends Object
    Contains the result of a show signature capture request finished after calling Terminal.showSignatureCapture(com.six.timapi.ShowSignatureCaptureRequest) or Terminal.showSignatureCaptureAsync(com.six.timapi.ShowSignatureCaptureRequest). Immutable class.
